###############################################################################
# Radish.Api - Wiki / Markdown API 测试
###############################################################################
# 说明：
# 1. PublicGet* 为匿名公开阅读契约，只返回 Published + Public + 未删除文档
# 2. Get* 浏览接口可携带普通登录 Token，按登录态与访问策略返回
# 3. 创建 / 更新 / 发布 / 导入 / 导出 建议使用 Admin / System Token
###############################################################################

@Access_Token = 在这里粘贴普通 access_token
@Admin_Access_Token = 在这里粘贴管理员 access_token
@Gateway_HostAddress = https://localhost:5000
@WikiDocumentId = 1
@WikiDocumentSlug = wiki-sample
@WikiRevisionId = 1
@WikiDraftId = 1
@WikiDraftVersion = 1

### 1. 获取公开文档列表（匿名，只返回 Published + Public）
GET {{Gateway_HostAddress}}/api/v1/Wiki/PublicGetList?pageIndex=1&pageSize=20
Accept: application/json

### 2. 获取公开文档树（匿名，只返回 Published + Public）
GET {{Gateway_HostAddress}}/api/v1/Wiki/PublicGetTree
Accept: application/json

### 3. 获取公开文档详情（匿名，只返回 Published + Public）
GET {{Gateway_HostAddress}}/api/v1/Wiki/PublicGetBySlug/{{WikiDocumentSlug}}
Accept: application/json

### 4. 获取文档列表（登录态访问策略）
GET {{Gateway_HostAddress}}/api/v1/Wiki/GetList?pageIndex=1&pageSize=20
Authorization: Bearer {{Access_Token}}
Accept: application/json

### 5. 获取文档树（登录态访问策略）
GET {{Gateway_HostAddress}}/api/v1/Wiki/GetTree
Authorization: Bearer {{Access_Token}}
Accept: application/json

### 6. 获取文档详情（按 ID）
GET {{Gateway_HostAddress}}/api/v1/Wiki/GetById/{{WikiDocumentId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{Access_Token}}
Accept: application/json

### 7. 获取文档详情（按 Slug）
GET {{Gateway_HostAddress}}/api/v1/Wiki/GetBySlug/{{WikiDocumentSlug}}
Authorization: Bearer {{Access_Token}}
Accept: application/json

### 8. 创建作者草稿（登录用户）
POST {{Gateway_HostAddress}}/api/v1/Wiki/AuthorCreate
Authorization: Bearer {{Access_Token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Wiki 示例文档",
  "slug": "wiki-sample",
  "summary": "用于验证 Wiki MVP 主链路",
  "markdownContent": "# Wiki 示例文档\n\n这是第一篇 Wiki 文档。",
  "changeSummary": "创建文档草稿"
}

### 9. 保存作者草稿（ExpectedDraftVersion 为 CAS 版本）
PUT {{Gateway_HostAddress}}/api/v1/Wiki/AuthorSaveDraft/{{WikiDraftId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{Access_Token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Wiki 示例文档（更新）",
  "slug": "wiki-sample",
  "summary": "用于验证 Wiki MVP 更新链路",
  "markdownContent": "# Wiki 示例文档\n\n这是更新后的内容。",
  "changeSummary": "补充说明",
  "expectedDraftVersion": {{WikiDraftVersion}}
}

### 10. 提交作者草稿审核
POST {{Gateway_HostAddress}}/api/v1/Wiki/AuthorSubmitDraft/{{WikiDraftId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{Access_Token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "expectedDraftVersion": {{WikiDraftVersion}},
  "changeSummary": "提交审核"
}

### 11. 发布文档（审核批准应用后独立执行）
POST {{Gateway_HostAddress}}/api/v1/Wiki/Publish/{{WikiDocumentId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{Admin_Access_Token}}
Accept: application/json

### 12. 转为草稿
POST {{Gateway_HostAddress}}/api/v1/Wiki/Unpublish/{{WikiDocumentId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{Admin_Access_Token}}
Accept: application/json

### 13. 归档文档
POST {{Gateway_HostAddress}}/api/v1/Wiki/Archive/{{WikiDocumentId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{Admin_Access_Token}}
Accept: application/json

### 14. 导入 Markdown
POST {{Gateway_HostAddress}}/api/v1/Wiki/ImportMarkdown
Authorization: Bearer {{Admin_Access_Token}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=RadishWikiBoundary

--RadishWikiBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="sort"

0
--RadishWikiBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="publishAfterImport"

true
--RadishWikiBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="wiki-import-sample.md"
Content-Type: text/markdown

# 导入示例

这是通过 http 文件导入的 Markdown 文档。
--RadishWikiBoundary--

### 15. 导出 Markdown
GET {{Gateway_HostAddress}}/api/v1/Wiki/ExportMarkdown/{{WikiDocumentId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{Admin_Access_Token}}
Accept: text/markdown

### 16. 获取版本历史列表
GET {{Gateway_HostAddress}}/api/v1/Wiki/GetRevisionList/{{WikiDocumentId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{Admin_Access_Token}}
Accept: application/json

### 17. 获取版本详情
GET {{Gateway_HostAddress}}/api/v1/Wiki/GetRevisionDetail/{{WikiRevisionId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{Admin_Access_Token}}
Accept: application/json

### 18. 按版本回滚
POST {{Gateway_HostAddress}}/api/v1/Wiki/Rollback/{{WikiRevisionId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{Admin_Access_Token}}
Accept: application/json
